On 7/2/06 3:31 PM, "Wayne" <mga60(-at-)optonline.net> wrote:

> Does anyone make or know someone who makes a T adapter for oil pressure
> senders (stock plus VDO sender for gauge) that can be used without modifying
> the tin or other components?

The VDO extension works fine if you use a dual pole sender: one pole for the
pressure gauge and one pole for the dash warning light. Then there is no
need for a tee.

